{
  "id": "adv_bond_szk_01_03",
  "title": "兵藤雫3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "わ～！　凄い凄い凄い！\nアイドルのグッズがこ～んなにいっぱい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~! Awesome‚ awesome‚ awesome!\nThere are so~ many idol goods!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.866667366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "最近、新しく出来たお店なんだけど、広いし\n品揃えもいい。今、一番ホットなスポット",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This store opened recently‚ but it's big and\nhas a great selection. It's the hottest spot right now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.866667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5333340327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "見たことないグッズもいっぱいあるね……！\nDaydreamさんのバンダナだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many goods I've never seen before…!\nEven a Daydream-san's bandana!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0333328883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それは、このお店だけのオリジナルグッズ\n事務所と契約して、グッズの企画と販売もしてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's an original goods exclusive to this store\nThey have a contract with the agency‚ so they also plan and sell goods",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333328883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4666687648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "え～！？　じゃあこのお店でしか買えないんだ！\n凄いな～！　これは絶対買って帰らないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~!?! So I can only buy it here!\nThat's amazing~! I absolutely have to buy one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4666687648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1333367031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのグッズもあるよ\nオリジナルのは、まだ作ってないみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There're also goods from Hoshimi Prods.\nThey don't have any original goods yet",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1333367031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4333311082
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！　じゃあ、今なら企画し放題ってこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What! So‚ does that mean I can plan as much as I want now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4333311082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8666685105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "し放題かは、分からないけど……提案してみるのは\nいいんじゃないかな。何か、アイデアがあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know if it's as much as you'd like… I think it's okay\nto suggest it. Do you have any ideas?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8666685105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4000010809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　ブリのぬいぐるみ、ってどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! How about‚ a yellowtail plushie?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4000010809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0333283108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんの恋愛ゲームが出た時に\nブリを売るシーンが好評だったみたいなんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Rei-chan's dating game came out‚\nthe scene where she sells yellowtail seemed to be well-received",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0333283108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1000000638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、コアなファンには好評だったけど……\nブリのぬいぐるみだと、怜ちゃんの要素が薄いかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it was well-received by core fans…\nIf it's a yellowtail plushie‚ Rei-chan's element might be faint",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1000000638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6000001908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、そう言われると思ってたよ\nだからね、ブリの顔を怜ちゃんにすればいいんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu‚ I thought you'd say that\nThen‚ just change the yellowtail's face to Rei-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.1666668575
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.1333279293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうすれば、怜ちゃんの要素もちゃんとあるし\nただのブリより可愛くなると思うんだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we do that‚ Rei-chan's elements will also fit in properly\nI think it'll be cuter than a normal yellowtail~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1333279293,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15800.004068900009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.1999939603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "う～、考えただけで、胸がキュンキュンしてきちゃった\n早速、{user}さんにメッセしよっと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~‚ just thinking about it‚ makes my heart flutter!\nI'll message {user}-san right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1999939603,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12533.338037899995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.1666668575
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.6999939603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……言ってみるのは、自由だと思うけど……\n……って、あれ。さくらちゃん、大変……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-Umm… I think speaking is free…\n…but‚ wait. Sakura-chan‚ something's wrong…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6999939603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4666606269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　わっ……なんか注目されちゃってる……！？\nご、ごめんね、声大きかったかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Whoa… we're getting attention…!?\nS-Sorry‚ I have spoken loudly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4666606269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.6333339057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "サニピがいる、って気付かれちゃったのかも……\nどうしよう……騒ぎになったら、お店の迷惑になる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe they noticed that Sunny Peace is here…\nWhat should we do… If it causes a commotion‚ it'll be a bother to the shop…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6333339057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.3000005724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……！　雫ちゃん、これで顔を隠そう……！\nほら、ちょうどいいところにうちわがあるよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…! Shizuku-chan‚ let's hide our faces with this…!\nLook‚ there's a fan right here…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3000005724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.7999975206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、さくらちゃん……\nあ……これ、怜ちゃんのうちわだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Sakura-chan…\nAh… this is a Rei-chan's fan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7999975206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.3999975206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "私のは琴乃ちゃんのだ。よし、これを顔に当てて……\nコトノ！　コトノ！　イマダケコトノ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mine is Kotono-chan. Okay‚ let's use this to cover our faces…\nKOTONO! KOTONO! KOTONO JUST FOR THIS TIME!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3999975206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.0333319982
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.7666682563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
